# Catch stale bookmarks to the old landing page URL
/landing.html    /    301

# Clean vendor URLs — lovehearth.co.uk/{slug} serves the permanent vendor page.
# MUST stay the last rule in this file.
#
# Non-forced 200 rewrite: Netlify only reaches it when no real file and no
# earlier rule has matched, so every root .html page, every asset and the rule
# above continue to win. The address bar is unchanged, so vendor.html reads the
# slug from location.pathname.
#
# Do not add a bang (!) and do not make this a 301/302. A forced rewrite would
# shadow real files; a redirect would rewrite the vendor's printed URL.
/*    /vendor.html   200
